dc_title_s: Hazard Stump Field: Mississippi River and Tributaries
dc_creator_sm: US Army Corps of Engineers, St. Paul District Office
dc_description_s: This is a polygon data layer of stump fields along the Minnesota River from Shakopee, MN, the St. Croix River (river mile 26), and the Mississippi River main channel from the Coon Rapids Dam to Pool 10 in the St. Paul District.
